ALECTOR demo corpus — attribution and license
==============================================

The file demo_corpora/alector.zip contains the ALECTOR corpus: 79 French
texts and their professionally simplified versions (NNN_source.txt /
NNN_target.txt), shipped as unmodified plain-text files.

Source
------
  Gala, N., Tack, A., Javourey-Drevet, L., François, T., & Ziegler, J. C.
  (2020). Alector: A parallel corpus of simplified French texts with
  alignments of misreadings by poor and dyslexic readers. Proceedings of
  the 12th Language Resources and Evaluation Conference (LREC 2020).
  https://aclanthology.org/2020.lrec-1.169/

